  "text": "Migration session log (2025-09-01):\n- Copied plan from Wiab.pro to local docs; it outlines phases A–F.\n- Implemented Task A (feature flags): Added enableQuasiDeletionUi, enableDynamicRendering, enableFragmentFetch to FlagConstants + ClientFlagsBase with defaults off; compile OK.\n- Implemented Task B (quasi adapter): Added QuasiConversationViewAdapter to emit pre/post delete events; created QuasiDeletable marker; wired adapter construction in StageTwo.install() behind flag.\n- Implemented Task C (deleted UI): Added BlipViewDomImpl#setQuasiDeleted and .blip.deleted CSS; subscribed quasi adapter in StageTwo to mark DOM before removal.\n- Implemented Task D (minimal): Added ScreenController interface + ScreenControllerImpl using Window scroll/resize; not yet wired.\n- Task E: scaffolded DynamicRenderer, DynamicRendererImpl, DynamicDomRenderer (placeholders), to be filled next.\n- Chose to integrate quasi UI with existing LiveConversationViewRenderer to meet DoD ahead of dynamic renderer.\n- Next: Map dependencies (RenderUtil, ElementMeasurer, DomScroller) and begin porting DynamicRendererImpl logic trimmed (no fragment fetch).",
